												</div>
												<div class="details">
													<h4><i class="fa fa-check"></i>Define Your Choices</h4>
													<p>Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry. Lorem Ipsum has been the industry's.</p>
												</div>
												
											</div>
										</div>
										<div class="col-md-12 col-lg-6">
											<img class="img img-fluid" src="theme_centric/static/src/img/service_detail1.jpg"/>
										</div>
									</div>
								</div>
								<div class="service-detail-area">
									<div class="row align-items-center">
										<div class="col-md-12 col-lg-6">
											<img class="img img-fluid" src="theme_centric/static/src/img/service_detail2.jpg"/>
										</div>
										<div class="col-md-12 col-lg-6">
											<div class="service-detail-content">
												
												<h3>Social Media Marketing</h3>
